<Weakness xmlns="http://cwe.mitre.org/cwe-7" xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" ID="704" Name="Incorrect Type Conversion or Cast" Abstraction="Class" Structure="Simple" Status="Incomplete">
         <Description>The product does not correctly convert an object, resource, or structure from one type to a different type.</Description>
